This page is meant to give AI authors and players alike a guide at hand on judging the completeness and competitiveness of AIs.

== Simple test ==
Grab the corresponding map, load it, start the AI (console: start_ai <name of AI>) and wait for 10 years. Judge the result by the following:
* Crash: -5 points
* running unprofitable or doing nothing: 0 points
* otherwise (i.e. making profit): points as indicated

=== Vehicle capabilities ===
* Ships: 5 points
* Road vehicles: 5 points
* Rail vehicles: 5+5 points (5 for usage, addition 5 for using more than point to point connections)
* Aircraft: 5 points

